Nraf counter and attack as Amazo 2.0

✯God Emperor doom✯

"As I suspected I was right all along huh? Good it seems My intuition was correct Now the time to finish this"

He uttered before a dark energy Appeared on his right hand he clenched the fist while Amazo's body was still heavy he clenched his fist causing Amazo's arms and legs to get ripped off and crushed he Controlled the heavy gravity magic at Amazo's throat Crushing it completely however he was not done there 

"This was educational Amazo you've taught me a few things or maybe one to be exact so let's finish this for both our sakes ok"

He uttered as his magic which entered Amazo's body before suddenly got pulled out it of Amazo's body He grabbed him by his face and slammed him hard on the ground crushing his head however doom was far from over he then Put two of his fingers Through Amazo's eyes crushing them and blinding him Doom grabbed him by his crushed throat and threw him up where the Barrier drained and electrocuted his body Amazo fell down and doom turned around awaiting to see if Amazo could stand up


"Hmmm was it wrong to bring the White hoodie and cape to a green place? Hmmm green is better for this one"

He uttered as the clothes changed colour they turned green and doom still did not stare at Amazo waiting to see what shall happen

✯God Emperor doom✯

He uttered as his magic which entered Amazo's body before suddenly got pulled out it of Amazo's body He grabbed him by his face and slammed him hard on the ground crushing his head however doom was far from over he then Put two of his fingers Through Amazo's eyes crushing them and blinding him Doom grabbed him by his crushed throat and threw him up where the Barrier drained and electrocuted his body Amazo fell down and doom turned around awaiting to see if Amazo could stand up
